{"word":"Raven","slug":"raven","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Raven</b> A black carnivorous bird<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=30&verse=17'>Pro 30:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=22&chapter=5&verse=11'>Son 5:11</a><br/> Forbidden as food<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=11&verse=15'>Lev 11:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=14&verse=14'>Deu 14:14</a><br/> Preserved by Noah in the ark<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=8&verse=7'>Gen 8:7</a><br/> Fed Elijah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=17&verse=6'>1Ki 17:6</a><br/> Cared for by divine providence<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=12&verse=24'>Luk 12:24</a>"}]}